        <Summary>A live stop motion animation software</Summary>
        <Description>Toonloop is a live stop motion animation software. It aims to show the creation process to the audience as well as the result of the creation. Frame by frame animations are made by adding frames one by one to a clip made of many frames. Clips are displayed in a never ending loop.</Description>
